'''Hrucium''' was an element used in heavy industry that became destabilized after use. It was released when [[Waste Canister Delivery Port 84-D-21]] in the [[Desrini District]] of [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] misfired. An isotope of hrucium, hrucium-5, was highly toxic. During the [[Cold War (Galactic Republic–Sith Empire)|Cold War]], a chemical freighter crashed on a [[Moon/Legends|moon]] and spilled large quantities of hrucium-5 onto the surface, damaging the wildlife and forcing the [[Arcona/Legends|Arcona]] [[Senaru]] to seek help off-world to save his community and their homeworld.

